OL,3,CParkinson's drug could be used to
OL,4,Ctreat depression
OL,6,FAn Oxfordshire man, who suffered with
OL,7,Fdepression for 20 years, says he's got
OL,8,Fhis life back after taking part in a
OL,9,Fground-breaking drug trial.
OL,11,FPhil Harvey was given Pramipexole, a
OL,12,Fdrug traditionally used to treat
OL,13,FParkinson's disease, as part of
OL,14,Fresearch by the University of Oxford.
OL,16,FHe saw an improvement in just a few
OL,17,Fweeks and three years later the 72-
OL,18,Fyear-old is still reaping the benefits.
