OL,6,F"Oh it's fantastic, I'm enjoying life
OL,7,Fagain. When I think I've missed 20
OL,8,Fyears of enjoyment, I'm making up for
OL,9,Fit now.
OL,11,F"I got myself a motorbike, I go out on
OL,12,Fonce a week. I try and play a guitar,
OL,13,FI've built a couple from kits, I love
OL,14,Fcooking. It's all come back."
OL,16,FFor two decades Phil suffered with
OL,17,Fdepression. He says he tried every
OL,18,Fkind of treatment going but nothing
OL,19,Fworked.
