OL,6,F"I was in a very dark place. If I got
OL,7,Fup in the mornings it was a bonus. If
OL,8,FI got up and went downstairs I sat in
OL,9,Fa chair and was just nowhere.
OL,11,F"I had no motivation, no interests, I
OL,12,Flost interest in doing all the hobbies
OL,13,Fand things like that. Nothing, nothing
OL,14,Fat all would pull me out of it."
OL,16,FBut that all changed when he was
OL,17,Finvited to take part in a drug trial
OL,18,Ffor treatment-resistant depression.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
