OL,4,Ctreat depression
OL,6,FHe was given Pramipexole, which is
OL,7,Ftraditionally used to treat
OL,8,FParkinson's Disease. It boosts
OL,9,Fdopamine which affects our experience
OL,10,Fof enjoyment.
OL,12,F"There was less tiredness, more
OL,13,Fmotivation, less feeling emotional.
OL,15,F"I mean, you get very emotional when
OL,16,Fyou're depressed, believe me, because
OL,17,Fyou sit there sometimes with tears
OL,18,Fstreaming down your face for no reason.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
