OL,6,F"And all that started to pick up.
OL,7,FProbably within about six to eight
OL,8,Fweeks I was living a reasonably normal
OL,9,Flifestyle again."
OL,11,FThe idea of trialling the drug came
OL,12,Ffrom Professor of psychiatry at the
OL,13,FUniversity of Oxford, Michael Browning.
OL,15,FThe research involved 150 patients.
OL,16,FOver the course of a year, half were
OL,17,Fgiven Pramipexole and half a placebo.
OL,19,FThe drug was discovered to be about
OL,20,Ftwice as effective as other treatments.
