OL,6,FProfessor Browning said: "I run a
OL,7,Fclinic for people with difficult to
OL,8,Ftreat depression, also that's the only
OL,9,Fsort of patient that I see.
OL,11,F"I have to say, I used this drug for a
OL,12,Fbit and it isn't subtle how effective
OL,13,Fthis drug is.
OL,15,F"Compared with the other treatments I
OL,16,Fuse it's obviously a lot better, so I
OL,17,Fwasn't surprised at how effective it
OL,18,Fwas in this study.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
