OL,6,F"I was worried that maybe I hadn't
OL,7,Fdone the study well enough to measure
OL,8,Fit so I was quite relieved to see the
OL,9,Fstudy was so positive.
OL,11,F"But this chimes with my clinical
OL,12,Fexperience. This is what I see when I
OL,13,Fuse this drug to treat patients. It is
OL,14,Freally an effective treatment."
OL,16,F"It's given me my life back," said Mr
OL,17,FHarvey, "That's the sheer simple
OL,18,Ffactor, it's given me a life back
OL,19,Fagain which I hadn't got."
